      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;european-school-of-magnetism&#34;&gt;&#xA;  European School of Magnetism&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#european-school-of-magnetism&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;2020---online&#34;&gt;&#xA;  2020 - Online&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#2020---online&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&#34;https://magnetism.eu/135-2020-school.htm&#34;&gt;2020 European School of Magnetism&lt;/a&gt; was held online.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I gave a 1.5-hour online lecture on &lt;strong&gt;Transport and spintronics&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://magnetism.eu/esm/2020/slides/kim-slides.pdf&#34;&gt;[pdf]&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;2018--krakow-poland&#34;&gt;&#xA;  2018 â€“ Krakow, Poland&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#2018--krakow-poland&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&#34;http://esm2018.agh.edu.pl/&#34;&gt;2018 European School of Magnetism&lt;/a&gt; was held in Krakow, Poland. I gave three 1.5-hour lectures on various aspects of magnetisation processes, including quasi-static processes, precessional dynamics, and spin-transfer torques.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The course outline and lecture notes are given below.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
